/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fdeclan-mckenna-tickets%2Fartist%2F2189205" target="_blank" rel="noopener">演出。任何最后一刻的门票</a>。</p><p>从那时起，Wunderhorse 将迎来一个繁忙的夏季，参加许多主要音乐节，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">Reading &amp; Leeds</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stormzy-chase-status-becky-hill-lead-boardmasters-2024-line-up-3551298">Boardmaster</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">TRNSMT</a> ，并在 Dot to Dot Festival 上首次亮相。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-wunderhorses-bluesy-new-single-midas-3616648">聆听 Wunderhorse 的布鲁斯新单曲“Midas”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
