-vamps">The Vamps</a>主唱）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frozemode">Frozemode</a> 、Jessie Murph、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/swim-school">Swim School</a> 、Dead Poet Society、The Luka State、The Oozes、Bears in Trees、ThxSoMch 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talk-show">脱口秀</a>、齐诺·芬奇、塞布·洛、好邻居、菲利克斯·艾姆斯等。</p><p>已宣布将在全新 Chevron 舞台上表演的新艺人包括 Jaguar、Mette、LeoStayTrill 和 Efan。新舞台还将在两个场地举办深夜表演，包括 Nathan Dawe 和力量民谣俱乐部之夜 Ultimate Power，为狂欢者带来音乐和歌声。</p><p> Sota、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/overmono">Overmono</a> 、Dr. Dubplate、DJ Semtex、it&#39;s murph、Oppidan、Notion、Yemz、Arthi、Chloe Caillet、Saint Ludo、Simula 和 Gia 也将在今年的音乐节上在粉丝最喜爱的利兹专属 LS23 舞台上表演。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5oTN2MoW8Y/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><